{"title":"西财烟火觅食记 ｜ 夜","uid":"e46c7d6360688848a6f6c9ce785d8deb","slug":"推文9","date":"2021-10-13T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:38:41.669Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文9.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231902607.png","content":"<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231811425.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231811425\"></p>\n<p>欢一个路灯到另一个路灯的距离</p>\n<p>因为那一段路有影子的陪伴</p>\n<p>—</p>\n<p>走进西财的夜</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231819297.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231819297\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231824346.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231824346\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231828908.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231828908\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231832425.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231832425\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231836947.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231836947\"></p>\n<p>我总是忍不住回想起那座城市的夜晚</p>\n<p>灯光燃成的篝火，我坐在天台上，时光短促又漫长</p>\n<p>风从我耳边流过带来整个世界的声音</p>\n<p>风中，有人弹唱，有人舞蹈，有人相爱</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231846842.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231846842\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231852635.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231852635\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231856004.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231856004\"></p>\n<p>一室秋灯，一庭秋雨</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231902607.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231902607\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231906172.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231906172\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231911804.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231911804\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231918115.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231918115\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231921430.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231921430\"></p>\n<p>我们在不同风景</p>\n<p>相同时光里</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231928711.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231928711\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231932386.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231932386\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231936472.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231936472\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231941273.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231941273\"></p>\n<p>一直想从你的窗子里看月亮</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231949314.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231949314\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231954194.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231954194\"></p>\n<p>明月当空，繁星点点</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232000445.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232000445\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232004684.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232004684\"></p>\n<p>山河远阔，烟火人间</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232012876.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232012876\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232018522.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232018522\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232022367.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232022367\"></p>\n<p>再好的文案，</p>\n<p>都不及这一刻的夜景和微风</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232031598.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232031598\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303232036828.png\" alt=\"image-20220303232036828\"></p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p><p>摄 | 赵书铮 罗昌嘉 肖博元 徐皓辰 钟志涛</p>\n<p>排版 | 卢江倩 李宜霏</p>\n</p>\n</details>\n","text":" 欢一个路灯到另一个路灯的距离 因为那一段路有影子的陪伴 — 走进西财的夜 我总是忍不住回想起那座城市的夜晚 灯光燃成的篝火，我坐在天台上，时光短促又漫长 风从我耳边流过带来整个世界的声音 风中，有人弹唱，有人舞蹈，有人相爱 一室秋灯，一庭秋雨 我们在不同风景 相同时光里 一直想...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":259,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财烟火","slug":"西财烟火","count":3,"path":"api/categories/西财烟火.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"西财影集｜风吹叶落","uid":"7333637bd0ac50daa267f8c488e27013","slug":"推文10","date":"2021-10-21T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:54:56.343Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文10.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235244320.png","text":"秋风烈酒，从此渐入深秋 已经到了闻糖炒栗子香剥橘子的天气 估计再过些天就要把手揣进兜里 呵着白气去买烤红薯 希望夏天的遗憾 是秋天惊喜的铺垫 他一个人肯定很冷吧 枫叶将黄未黄 摇曳不定 像是不安的心 风吹叶落 和煦阳光下 猫在小憩 感谢 摄｜易钰垒 李宜霏 赵书铮 钟志涛 肖博元...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":172,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财影集","slug":"西财影集","count":3,"path":"api/categories/西财影集.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"秋","slug":"秋","count":5,"path":"api/tags/秋.j